{
  "text": "c-myc [CITATION_1] , the viral oncoprotein E1A (10), or \u00df-catenin (11). There are no similar data available for Reptin. On the other hand, in various assays, Reptin was found to antagonize the transcriptional effect of the TCF/LEF-1-\u00df-catenin complex, whereas Pontin potentiated it (8).",
